- DIANE: <i>How are you 2?</i>

780
00:39:21.150 --> 00:39:22.730
<i>That address turn up anything?</i>

781
00:39:22.740 --> 00:39:24.320
We think the Campbells found evidence...

782
00:39:24.320 --> 00:39:26.280
that the metro bomb was for a different target.

783
00:39:26.280 --> 00:39:27.240
What do you mean?

784
00:39:27.240 --> 00:39:28.570
Something above ground.

785
00:39:28.570 --> 00:39:31.240
I'm confused. That line doesn't run above ground.

786
00:39:31.240 --> 00:39:34.750
I'll explain it better in person. but we think there will be another attack.

787
00:39:34.750 --> 00:39:35.830
Jesus.

788
00:39:36.370 --> 00:39:38.500
Peter. we need to share this with the FBI.

789
00:39:38.500 --> 00:39:40.500
<i>End of day. understood?</i>

790
00:39:41.170 --> 00:39:42.000
Understood.

791
00:39:52.430 --> 00:39:53.850
ERIK: Does this open?

792
00:39:53.850 --> 00:39:58.650
It's just office hours. I'm in here every day.

793
00:40:00.060 --> 00:40:01.570
Okay. we're good.

794
00:40:08.780 --> 00:40:10.160
You got your panic button?

795
00:40:11.240 --> 00:40:12.870
[ ♪ UNSETTLING MUSIC ♪ ]

796
00:40:15.830 --> 00:40:17.500
Yes. Thanks.

797
00:40:17.500 --> 00:40:19.380
[ ♪ DRAMATIC MUSIC ♪ ]

798
00:40:22.500 --> 00:40:25.000
[DOOR CLOSING]
- Sorry. the new guy's extra.

799
00:40:25.010 --> 00:40:26.760
Nah. it's his job to protect you.

800
00:40:27.260 --> 00:40:28.760
Like a warden to his inmates.

801
00:40:31.680 --> 00:40:34.600
I just wanted to say I'm sorry.

802
00:40:35.180 --> 00:40:36.770
I feel bad about yesterday...

803
00:40:36.770 --> 00:40:40.060
and I just don't want you to be. like. freaked out or...

804
00:40:41.980 --> 00:40:44.150
[BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY]

805
00:40:44.150 --> 00:40:45.230
I shouldn't be doing this.

806
00:40:45.230 --> 00:40:47.900
We need to keep talking. or he might start to think that...

807
00:40:47.900 --> 00:40:49.410
That this is happening.

808
00:40:52.740 --> 00:40:57.200
If someone finds out. I'll lose my job.
and you'll be in the middle of a scandal.

809
00:40:57.200 --> 00:40:58.660
I can't do that to you.

810
00:40:59.620 --> 00:41:02.130
Well. what if we could be alone for a couple hours?

811
00:41:02.630 --> 00:41:04.670
Somewhere private. maybe your place?

812
00:41:04.670 --> 00:41:05.630
Right.

813
00:41:05.630 --> 00:41:08.510
And Secret Service will just wait outside the door while we...

814
00:41:08.510 --> 00:41:09.630
While we what?

815
00:41:12.970 --> 00:41:14.720
No one can find out about this.

816
00:41:15.470 --> 00:41:16.310
No one.

817
00:41:17.180 --> 00:41:19.810
You told me to trust my instincts. You should too.

818
00:41:22.020 --> 00:41:24.190
I can ditch the Agents. I've done it before.

819
00:41:24.190 --> 00:41:27.070
I... I swear. we'll be all alone.

820
00:41:29.240 --> 00:41:31.240
If it's what you want.

821
00:41:33.910 --> 00:41:35.740
[ ♪ DRAMATIC MUSIC ♪ ]

822
00:41:37.330 --> 00:41:39.330
[BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY]

823
00:41:44.080 --> 00:41:45.540
CHELSEA: How's the shoulder?

824
00:41:45.540 --> 00:41:47.210
All good. Thanks.

825
00:41:48.460 --> 00:41:49.590
I'm curious.

826
00:41:49.590 --> 00:41:52.840
What did it feel like. taking that hit in Ohio?

827
00:41:55.850 --> 00:41:58.060
Um. it hurt.

828
00:41:59.180 --> 00:42:00.560
I mean. I know that sounds obvious...

829
00:42:00.560 --> 00:42:03.270
but I remember being weirdly surprised by that.

830
00:42:03.270 --> 00:42:05.520
Not exactly sure what I expected...

831
00:42:05.520 --> 00:42:09.110
but I guess some people black out. some go into shock.

832
00:42:09.110 --> 00:42:10.030
Me?

833
00:42:11.360 --> 00:42:13.400
All I remember is the pain.

834
00:42:13.410 --> 00:42:14.620
Would you do it again?

835
00:42:19.160 --> 00:42:23.250
Listen. maybe I do need this job to stay clean. all right?

836
00:42:24.670 --> 00:42:25.580
Maybe I do.

837
00:42:26.340 --> 00:42:28.920
But that still doesn't mean that I'm not up to it.

838
00:42:29.510 --> 00:42:31.550
The bar was a mistake. I own that.

839
00:42:31.550 --> 00:42:33.220
Don't question my commitment.

840
00:42:34.050 --> 00:42:37.260
My approach is different than yours and maybe even antiquated...

841
00:42:37.260 --> 00:42:39.180
but I will adapt.

842
00:42:40.810 --> 00:42:42.180
Here comes Harper.

843
00:42:42.180 --> 00:42:43.730
Hey. How's it going?

844
00:42:49.780 --> 00:42:50.940
[KEYBOARD CLACKING]

845
00:42:51.440 --> 00:42:54.900
No suspicious black jackets on video in the days leading up to the attack.

846
00:42:54.910 --> 00:42:56.320
What about the morning of?

847
00:42:56.320 --> 00:42:57.740
Yeah. that's where I'm at.

848
00:42:58.280 --> 00:43:01.120
Just some woman sitting in that café for 5 hours...

849
00:43:01.120 --> 00:43:03.750
staring out the window and talking to herself.

850
00:43:05.670 --> 00:43:06.500
Show me.

851
00:43:07.000 --> 00:43:08.380
[ ♪ TENSE MUSIC ♪ ]

852
00:43:08.380 --> 00:43:09.460
[KEYBOARD CLACKING]

853
00:43:12.550 --> 00:43:15.260
She's not talking to herself. She's talking into a mic.

854
00:43:15.880 --> 00:43:16.720
Zoom in.

855
00:43:17.550 --> 00:43:18.890
Hold on. I'll sharpen it.

856
00:43:20.390 --> 00:43:22.390
How could you be sure they aren't on the right track?

857
00:43:22.390 --> 00:43:25.230
Because my operatives already spoke to the woman in question.

858
00:43:25.230 --> 00:43:27.190
She gave up what little info she had.

859
00:43:27.190 --> 00:43:28.270
Sutherland and the girl...

860
00:43:28.270 --> 00:43:30.230
are not close enough for us to be worried yet.

861
00:43:30.230 --> 00:43:32.530
And what happened to her? The woman.

862
00:43:33.490 --> 00:43:35.700
MAN: <i>Probably best not to say.</i>

863
00:43:35.700 --> 00:43:36.950
[SIGHING] Jesus.

864
00:43:37.450 --> 00:43:40.240
You wanted loose ends tied up.
- Yeah. yeah. yeah. I get it.

865
00:43:41.120 --> 00:43:42.870
When is this all gonna be over?

866
00:43:42.870 --> 00:43:44.040
Soon.

867
00:43:45.580 --> 00:43:47.920
Okay. what am I looking for?
- Shit.

868
00:43:47.920 --> 00:43:48.830
ROSE: What?

869
00:43:50.000 --> 00:43:51.290
She's Secret Service.

870
00:43:51.300 --> 00:43:52.750
How could you be so sure?

871
00:43:52.760 --> 00:43:54.340
'Cause I know her.

872
00:43:56.880 --> 00:43:59.180
[ ♪ SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC SWELLING ♪ ]

873
00:44:05.270 --> 00:44:06.940
Good morning. Mr. Vice President.

874
00:44:08.270 --> 00:44:10.550
Good morning. She in there? I got this.
- CHELSEA: Yes.

875
00:44:12.150 --> 00:44:15.940
Okay. if she's Secret Service. then that means...

876
00:44:15.940 --> 00:44:17.950
She's on somebody's protection detail.

877
00:44:18.950 --> 00:44:20.950
Rose. this isn't a terrorist attack anymore...

878
00:44:20.950 --> 00:44:22.830
this is an assassination attempt.

879
00:44:23.540 --> 00:44:24.500
On who?

880
00:44:25.700 --> 00:44:26.910
REDFIELD: Hey. sweetie.

881
00:44:27.960 --> 00:44:29.210
Already with the look.

882
00:44:29.210 --> 00:44:31.460
MADDIE: We both know why you're here. so get on with it.

883
00:44:31.460 --> 00:44:34.460
I went to a bar. a guy talked to me.
- REDFIELD: Maddie...

884
00:44:34.460 --> 00:44:37.510
REDFIELD: Why do you have to go out of your way to have problems?

885
00:44:37.510 --> 00:44:40.680
MADDIE: How is going to a bar going out of my way to have problems?

886
00:44:40.680 --> 00:44:43.510
REDFIELD: You don't need to go to a bar! Why don't you try studying?

887
00:44:43.520 --> 00:44:44.850
[ ♪ MUSIC FADES ♪ ]

